Welcome to TW5 Pocket-io.

This system networks together multiple 'server' editon TiddlyWikis. This is done using WikiText client-side and JavaScript server-side. The JavaScript code is stored in wikis as tiddlers and uploaded to the server on-demand and upon startup.

