To add a wiki to the network copy the 'server' edition wiki directory (one containing the 'tiddlywiki.info' file) to the project './wikis' directory.

Can add a new wiki using the standard `tiddlywiki ./wikis/myWiki --init server` command from the project directory. The wiki will be added on startup.


